 in level (which provide some great looking animations). Monks also get some excellent 1HB weapons, so many monks are now using some weapons.  &lt;strong&gt;Monks dish out some incredible damage, since they get dual wield and double attack very early,&lt;/strong&gt; resulting in many attacks per round.  No other tank class can match them at this.........&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;So to sum up, I think we should be higher straight DPS than a rouge, and let them have the higher Special attacks. As was intended by design so not that much of a stretch to ask for.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Soulfyst&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
