&lt;DIV&gt;I am also well aware that I am not representative for the majority of casuals, I just refuse to be part of the raiding game. But opposite to you and some others I am not totally out of touch with them either and I don't think that I am&amp;nbsp;anything special just because I manage to&amp;nbsp;put in some time in a game.&amp;nbsp;There is a reason I have 7.1 years on my monk, that I have had up to 6 accounts and that I still care for EQ. You guys just refuse to gasp that EQ is not only about the lvl 70, 500+ AA raiding crowd. You won't be happy before the last casual left the game or shuts his mouth.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
